MENU FILE HEADER (Don't delete)
MENU FILE NAME: $popcontrib/x/xved/doit_menus/delete_menu
Delete line                                 !!  RETURNAFTER vedlinedelete
Undo it                                     !!  RETURNAFTER ved_yankl
Delete line to left                         !!  RETURNAFTER vedclearhead
Undo it                                     !!  RETURNAFTER ved_yankw
Delete line to right                        !!  vedcleartail
Undo it                                     !!  RETURNAFTER ved_yankw

Delete word left                            !!  RETURNAFTER vedwordleftdelete
Undo it                                     !!  RETURNAFTER ved_yankw
Delete word right                           !!  RETURNAFTER vedwordrightdelete
Undo it                                     !!  RETURNAFTER ved_yankw
Delete marked range                         !!  ved_d
Undo it                                     !!  ved_y
Delete everything in file                   !!  ved_clear
Undo it                                     !!  ved_y

Delete file from disk                       !!  sysdelete(%vedpathname%) <> erase

Delete up to string                         !!  ENTER 'ds '

Menu menu      ----->                       !!  'menu menu'
